#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.28:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga "
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Lokasutta "
msgstr "28. The World "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.176, sc1
msgctxt "sn47.28:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ. "
msgstr "The same setting. "

msgctxt "sn47.28:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

#. VAR: katamesaṃ, āvuso anuruddha → āyasmā anuruddho (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn47.28:1.3"
msgid "“katamesaṃ, āvuso anuruddha, dhammānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend Anuruddha, what things have you developed and cultivated to attain great direct knowledge?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.28:1.4"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto. "
msgstr "“Reverend, I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.28:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.28:2.2"
msgid "Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, kāye kāyānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when I meditate observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.28:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "I meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.28:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.28:2.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.28:2.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ khvāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā mahābhiññataṃ patto. "
msgstr "I attained great direct knowledge by developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.28:2.7"
msgid "Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā sahassaṃ lokaṃ abhijānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that I directly know the entire galaxy.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.28:2.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
